      "description": "Fate: 43.58% applied to cropland, 56.42% sold for fertilizer",
      "methodClassification": "estimated with assumptions",
      "methodClassificationDescription": "In light of low data resolution/quality with respect to reported quantities of manure removed from facilities, a standard excretion rate was assumed for both pullet and layer facilities based on Pelletier et al. (2014b) (reflecting US production), and scaled relative to reported feed conversion efficiencies.",
      "transport": [
        {
          "term": {
            "@type": "Term",
            "termType": "transport",
